entry.notes:
Not just for anchors
	hrefs: hover can be used with other elements! E.g., 

	#kb_table th:hover {
		background-color: green;
		color: #FFFFFF;
		font-size: 1.5em;
	}

This eliminates need to call 'onmouseover' and 'onmouseout'  to deal with dynamic styling; Also, this leaves javascript function clear to focus on 'onclick' scripting.

"mysqli_query($link, ""CREATE TABLE myCity LIKE City"");
$query = ""INSERT INTO myCity VALUES (NULL, 'Stuttgart', 'DEU', 'Stuttgart', 617000)"";
mysqli_query($link, $query);
printf (""New Record has id %d.\n"", mysqli_insert_id($link));"
